.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REBALANCE-REPORT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-rebalance-report \- report channel liquidity imbalances
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-rebalance-report
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes per-channel local ratio (local_msat / total_msat) and labels each
channel as
.BR local_heavy ,
.BR remote_heavy ,
or
.BR balanced .
Results are sorted by distance from the ideal 50/50 balance, worst first.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, local_ratio, local_msat, total_msat, imbalance}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-rebalance (1),
.BR lightning-liquidity-report (1)
